<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>91</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Amah umna munthip achun ei sel ina,
 Khawvel thil ngaihtuoh na puokgik apat in;
 A zahngaihna limnuoi ah nuom takin chawl ka,
 Zie chun ka Tanpa'n ei veng ina.

[V2]
 Bit takin kei eisel ina,
 Lungkhamna, thepna sukbuoi phak lohna munah;
 Bit takin kei ei sel ina!
 Amah umna munthip achun ei sel ina.

[V3]
 2. Amah umna munthip achun ei-sel ina,
 A lopina pak chu ei muhsak intin;
 Amah chun vakna'n puon bangin ei thuom intin,
 Aw ka tha a kipak na ding e!

[V4]
 3. Amah umna munthip a chun ei sel ina,
 A hehpihna hai ngeilo, munthip a chun;
 Ka Hukdampa tawh kiho in cheng khawm ung kau,
 Chunggam nawpna teplawkna ahi.</lyrics>
<title>HE WILL SAFELY HIDE ME</title>
</song>